          <h2>GST refund restriction with regard to input services is constitutionally valid</h2>
          <amp-img src="file:///C:/Users/User/Desktop/Caro%202020/This_week_Newsletter/Refund.svg"
              width="100" height="120"
              layout="responsive">
          </amp-img>
          <p>While disposing of the bunch of writ petitions in a matter relating to refund of Input Tax Credit under Inverted Duty Structure scheme, the Madras High Court held that the refund restriction with regard to input services under the inverted duty structure scheme is valid and constitutional.</p>
        </amp-story-grid-layer>
      </amp-story-page>

      <!-- Page 4 (Rabbit): 3 layers (fill (video) + vertical + vertical) -->
