          <h2>Key highlights of the FCRA (Amendment) Bill, 2020</h2>
          <amp-img src="file:///C:/Users/User/Desktop/Caro%202020/This_week_Newsletter/Key_highlights_for_Bill.svg"
              width="100" height="120"
              layout="responsive">
          </amp-img>
          <p>The amendments in the FCRA will help in checking the misuse of foreign funds by receiving entities. Besides, it will enable the Government to keep a close watch on the undesirable activities of NGOs receiving overseas funding.</p>
        </amp-story-grid-layer>
      </amp-story-page>

      <!-- Page 5 (Collage): 2 layers + animations -->
