          <h2>Delhi HC admits petition challenging Rule 90(3) of the CGST Rules</h2>
          <amp-img src="file:///C:/Users/User/Desktop/Caro%202020/This_week_Newsletter/Law_court.svg"
              width="100" height="120"
              layout="responsive">
          </amp-img>
          <p>Hon’ble Delhi High Court has admitted a petition with regard to refund of excess GST which was inadvertently paid by the petitioner. The High Court has issued notices to Government and listed the case to be heard on December 9, 2020.</p>
        </amp-story-grid-layer>
      </amp-story-page>

      <!-- End of page-5-->

      <!-- Page 6 (Collage): 2 layers + animations -->
      <amp-story-page id="page3">
