          <h2> DAAB proposed six Forensic Accounting and Investigation Standards (FAISs) </h2>
          <amp-img src="file:///C:/Users/User/Desktop/Caro%202020/This_week_Newsletter/Accounting.svg"
              width="100" height="120"
